{"tid":1381134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦：堅決支持林鄭月娥依法施政　警方嚴正執法","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:29:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13f1c78e197c293429b2327c1e627efd22c074b8","tid":1381134,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1471147_1_20190729151638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1471147_1_20190729151638.jpg&h=64eb50c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港澳辦發言人楊光表示，希望香港社會盡快走出政治紛爭，集中精力發展經濟，改善民生，香港雖然積累一些不錯的家底，具有一些有利務件和獨特優勢，但也經不起折騰，香港亂下去，全社會都要「買單」。<br />\n<br />\n楊光又表示，中央政府將繼續堅定不移貫徹一國兩制方針，堅持一國兩制方針不會變，不動搖，確保一國兩制堅持實踐不走樣，不變形。<br />\n<br />\n楊光又表示，相信在中央政府和祖國內地的大力支持下，在行政長官林鄭月娥和特區政府的帶領下，香港能夠把香港管理好，建設好，發展好，香港一定能夠戰勝前進道路上的各種困難和挑戰，一國兩制這艘航船一定能夠劈波斬浪，行穩致遠。"},{"pid":"00353232a514f89967456563d511715bc1e23377","tid":1381134,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:22:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1147004&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1147004%26csid%3D261_341&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=dddd2a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1147004&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1d86ea018f9e4c8ed4a7bf1b849acb0db8a294b0","tid":1381134,"uid":108814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da4f9e6753d1da4083d04dc8277d39d2dab3ee3","tid":1381134,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"nothing new"},{"pid":"4197f62561ec8d6